name: Who Works Around You
overview:
Who Works Around You is Singapore’s first online community for working singles featuring location-based matching that connects people working around their vicinity. Using any web enabled device such as a laptop, PDA or mobile phone, you can now find a date around your workplace easily!

Being of one of the pioneer recipients of the Partner Connection Fund from Social Development Unit (SDU) of Singapore in 2007, we strive to provide an innovative approach, building a community of working singles who wish to widen their social circles and eventually increase the chances of finding their life partners. This portal matches members not only by their submitted personal profiles but also with their work location geo-data.

SDU Trust

On the 5th November 2008, Who Works Around You marked another milestone by joining 6 other dating agencies in receiving their SDU Trust accreditation after going through more than 6 months of trainings and assessments. [what is SDU Trust?]
